12\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\">Porph.</author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Plot.\">Plot.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">12</biblScope> </bibl>:—<tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">feel awe</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">fear</tr_> before God,<tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">feel shame</tr_>, <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">οὔ νυ σέβεσθε</foreign>; <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0012.tlg001.perseus-grc1:4:242\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Il.\">Il.</a></author> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">4.242</biblScope></bibl>, cf. <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0019.tlg003.perseus-grc1:293\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Ar.\">Ar.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Nu.\">Nu.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">293</biblScope> </bibl>; <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">τιμῶν καὶ σεβόμενος</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0059.tlg034.perseus-grc1:729c\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIform=\"author\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Pl.\">Pl.</a></author> <title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Lg.\">Lg.</a></title_> <biblScope TEIform=\"biblScope\">729c</biblScope> </bibl> </cit>; <foreign lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"foreign\">σεφθεῖσα</foreign> <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">awe-stricken</tr_>, Id.<title_ TEIform=\"title\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ Phdr.\">Phdr.</a></title_> l.c.: rarely c. <mood opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"mood\"><a class=\"S\" href=\"S:LSJ inf.\">inf.</a></mood>, <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">dread</tr_> or <tr_ opt=\"n\" TEIform=\"tr\">fear to do</tr_> a thing, <cit TEIform=\"cit\"> <quote_ lang=\"greek\" TEIform=\"quote\">ς. προσιδέσθαι . ., ἀντία φάσθαι</quote_> <bibl n=\"urn:cts:greekLit:tlg0085.tlg002.perseus-grc1:694\" default=\"NO\" TEIform=\"bibl\"> <author TEIfor